Chat with AI

=======================================

![Image 2: App screenshots](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/lifehacker-light.png)![Image 3: App screenshots](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/lifehacker-dark.png)

Jan is an open source ChatGPT-alternative that runs 100% offline.

[Download for Linux (deb)](https://github.com/janhq/jan/releases/download/v0.5.15/jan-linux-amd64-0.5.15.deb)

2.8M+¬†downloads | Free & Open Source

![Image 4: App screenshots](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/glow.png)![Image 5: App screenshots](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/glow.png)![Image 6: App screenshots](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/app-frame-light-fixed.png)![Image 7: App screenshots](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/app-frame-light-fixed.png)

100% Open Source
================

Our core team believes that AI should be open,  
and Jan is built in public

[###### Github 27.8K stars](https://github.com/janhq/jan)[###### Discord 1.3K online](https://discord.gg/FTk2MvZwJH)[###### Hugging Face 71 models](https://huggingface.co/janhq)

Features
========

01
==

###### Chat with AI

Ask your questions, brainstorm, and learn from the AI running on your device to be more productive.

![Image 8: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features01.png)![Image 9: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features01dark.png)

02
==

###### Model Hub

Download and Run powerful models like Llama3, Gemma or Mistral on your computer.

![Image 10: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features02.png)![Image 11: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features02dark.png)

03
==

###### Connect to Cloud AIs

You can also route to more powerful cloud models, like OpenAI, Groq, Cohere etc., when needed.

![Image 12: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features03.png)![Image 13: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features03dark.png)

04
==

###### Local API Server

Set up and run your own OpenAI-compatible API server using local models with just one click.

![Image 14: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features04.png)![Image 15: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features04dark.png)

05
==

###### Chat with your files

Experimental

Set up and run your own OpenAI-compatible API server using local models with just one click.

![Image 16: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features05.png)![Image 17: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features05dark.png)

![Image 18: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features01.png)![Image 19: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/features01dark.png)

Highly Customizable
===================

Customize Jan to match your needs and preferences.

Assistants & Memory
===================

Coming Soon

Create personalized AI assistants that remember your conversations and execute specific tasks across your systems.

![Image 20: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/assistant-light.png)![Image 21: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/assistant-dark.png)

Extensions
==========

Customize Jan with Extensions, that range from Cloud AI connectors, tools, data connectors.

![Image 22: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/extension-light.png)![Image 23: App Screenshot Feature](https://jan.ai/assets/images/homepage/extension-dark.png)

Our Principles
==============

Jan is opinionated software on what AI should be

##### Local-first

We believe your conversations and files should remain yours alone. That's why we prioritize local-first AI, running open-source models directly on your computer.

##### User-owned

Your data, your rules. Jan stores everything on your device in universal formats, giving you total freedom to move your data without tricks or traps.

##### Fully Customizable

You can endlessly customize the experience with 3rd party extensions. You can adjust alignment, moderation, and censorship levels to your needs.
